      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. It has been exceptionally well maintained and runs flawlessly with no mechanical issues. The interior is clean and undamaged with no visible wear, and the exterior is free of dents, scratches, or rust. All systems are functioning properly.",
